When Sun Devil fans think of Mo Latu, they think of the 6'2'' 370-pound defensive lineman that holds down the middle of ASU's defensive line. 
He's so much more than that though. 
Latu is a father to two young daughters and a family man at heart. 
He says no matter how things go on the football field, his daughters always make him smile and they make all the pain ease away. 
Latu may be an imposing force on the field, but at home he's the ultimate dad and husband. Read or Share this story: http://12ne.ws/1LBdV8q TOP VIDEOS
